{"tid":589784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"服了！中國特種兵 零下27°游水渡河","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T08:24:17.000Z","uid":54373,"like":295,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"aa00174c37926818fbb373f43275574226288467","tid":589784,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(神跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條河唔會結冰)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n來源：解放軍報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img9.itiexue.net/1727/17270793.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg9.itiexue.net%2F1727%2F17270793.jpg&h=124a375e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n............<br />\n<br />\n那年大年初一，合家團圓之時，團長李建軍卻帶領13名官兵穿梭在土耳其寒冷的原始森林中，接受國際特種兵集訓考核。<br />\n<br />\n飢餓，嚴寒，險阻，數倍於己的假設敵層層設阻，步步追殺。他們經過四天三夜連續行軍作戰，在耗盡所有給養後，終於準時到達了登機點。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到，此時土耳其考官突然宣布：登機點暴露，向20公里之外的臨時登機點轉移。<br />\n<br />\n冰天雪地，他們咬牙堅持，隱蔽轉移在離臨時登機點還剩3公里時，一條冰河橫亙在面前當時氣溫-27℃，團長李建軍果斷命令：。馬上泅渡過河。<br />\n<br />\n闖過冰河，他們披著一身冰甲，向終點拼命衝去......最終，他們成了這次考核中唯一完成任務的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n為了勝利，他們一往無前;為了勝利，他們一無所惜。"},{"pid":"9e9ac0178ddb9f3de5beec11aef15fb50c4456df","tid":589784,"uid":84275,"like":495,"dislike":2,"score":493,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"河面結冰，一定係一路破冰一路游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe5b9e6a2b395e0fb8c73f9bb1b87b3c7a7c3ca","tid":589784,"uid":653,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:47:46.000Z","msg":"。。。。"},{"pid":"2033de6f7c5d5f0f32fe5509c362de566c10425d","tid":589784,"uid":54373,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"quote":{"pid":"9e9ac0178ddb9f3de5beec11aef15fb50c4456df","tid":589784,"uid":84275,"like":495,"dislike":2,"score":493,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"河面結冰，一定係一路破冰一路游<img src=\"/ass